      <title>华尔街延续涨势，亚洲股市上涨：市场综述</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-05/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在受到关税、科技公司盈利不佳和美国经济数据不均衡等影响的一周内，华尔街股市和债券市场上涨，亚洲股市周四上涨。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-05/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 05 Feb 2025 22:37:06 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Costco 应该解释其 DEI 政策</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2025-02-05/costco-should-explain-its-dei-policies-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[使用 DEl 作为统称只会给反觉醒势力提供弹药。相反，Costco 应该告诉我们更多关于其实际政策的信息，彭博社观点专栏作家 Beth Kowitt 解释道。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2025-02-05/costco-should-explain-its-dei-policies-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 05 Feb 2025 22:32:25 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>贝森特表示，他和特朗普关注的是 10 年期收益率，而不是美联储</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-05/bessent-says-he-trump-focus-on-10-year-yields-not-pushing-fed</link>
      <description><![CDATA[财政部长斯科特·贝森特 (Scott Bessent) 表示，特朗普政府降低借贷成本的重点是 10 年期国债收益率，而不是美联储的基准短期利率。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-05/bessent-says-he-trump-focus-on-10-year-yields-not-pushing-fed</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 05 Feb 2025 21:31:59 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>麦格理关闭美国债务资本市场，以应对私人信贷转型</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-05/macquarie-shuts-us-debt-capital-markets-in-private-credit-pivot</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，麦格理集团有限公司 (Macquarie Group Ltd.) 正在关闭其美国债务资本市场部门，该部门的业务包括杠杆贷款发放、银团贷款和交易，以将资源集中在私人信贷上。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-05/macquarie-shuts-us-debt-capital-markets-in-private-credit-pivot</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 05 Feb 2025 14:10:20 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>摩根士丹利因需求激增而出售 55 亿美元 X 债券</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-04/morgan-stanley-boosts-x-debt-sale-as-investors-embrace-musk-bet</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，在投资者需求强于预期后，由摩根士丹利牵头的几家银行出售了与伊隆马斯克的社交媒体平台 X 相关的 55 亿美元债务。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-04/morgan-stanley-boosts-x-debt-sale-as-investors-embrace-musk-bet</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 04 Feb 2025 18:51:45 GMT</pubDate>
